{"type": "article", "id": 27160, "title": "Instagram改Logo之后，一堆人自发演绎或重做了一个", "description": "怎么感觉新 Logo 洗脑力如此之强。他们究竟在表达爱还是恨？", "date": "2016-05-22T07:12:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 26, "name": "instagram"}], "category": 17, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 246, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134348eq3FoWuazviBlIY0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>“无论批评赞美，人们对品牌 logo 指手画脚已经成为一个越来越明显的趋势。” 上周 Instagram 终于换掉它的宝丽来 icon 时，创新咨询公司 IDEO 的沟通设计主管 Remy Jauffret 对《好奇心日报》这么说。<br> </p>\n<p>除了大部分表示“好丑不想更新”的网友，一周过去，一大堆艺术家和设计师已经用创作表达了对新 icon 的看法，一般来说，“重新演绎”可以算得上点赞，“重新设计”就可以算是踩。 </p>\n<p>我们收集了一些根据 Instagram 新 icon 启发而进行的创作，动用的工具，有布料、花卉、工艺材料甚至食物，当然也有 PS 和 AI。虽然不知道客户的 Brief 就开始设计，有点不太公平，但这样的反馈至少相对积极，让我们看看人们对这款颇受争议的 icon 自己的理解。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134335abWPnxdq7M8D4tYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@el.garrobo</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134336xVg72hC58HFR3O1p.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@mimivelarde</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134336gVlGE6vFNUHxZ7Ru.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@deliciousmartha</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134337rAOhb3d97QpSxwaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@spinstamatic</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134337tC2MYKa1Pu7rZX6x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@bentomonsters</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134338d5hnw8UKq4piXOoL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@mydailypantone</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134339diHJc4UxFOW6bhmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@ Jack Kendall.</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134339qnkoUBGei6QzKt5M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@Michael Flarup </div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">⬆️这是很多人呼吁的一款设计，简单地把宝丽来拍扁。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134340pwqbIyFPYMt8KxuV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">@safa paksu</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134341WhXu8xUjHJ7S0Y2Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@Desiree Grace Tan</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134341FWrufhtKXdBNqznV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@Roman Menshikov.</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134342m5gI8e24dsSxfzUp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">@Sam Bunny</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">???</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134342feHDdNEYmgSo9lFX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">@Enon</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">把彩虹渐变和反白的位置替换一下，是很多人采用的方案。</p>\n<p class=\"\">下面是更多新图标的重新演绎，从被复制和传播的角度来看，新图标的洗脑力还是很高。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021343431ySK5sGrLVo9P2Bk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@5ftinf</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134344u68JM0l3BF9HvTXI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@jarrett.hendrix</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021343450wMaFLCNo2KqyWAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@tashalakoz</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134346yev7NLlKMUw9OjFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@esposin x @cukingcocinadereyes</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134347t0UeYNhdvSg6GfAr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@esposin x @cukingcocinadereyes</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134347wmoWxrVgGBhDS6MA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">@joselourenco</div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n\n"}